channel.title: Could someone help me/learn me coding?
channel.description:
Hello,
I have no experience with coding, but i would like to learn it. I want to make a RSPS and i'm looking for someone who can help me with that and who is trusted. O-T: I've tried to make a RSPS but it's only online for myself (my IP), allthough i did portforwart, maybe i failed. I don't know.
Don't know if this is the right section, if it's not move it please.
Thanks, Tim
EDIT: i used this guide to make my RSPS [url=http://forum.ragezone.com/f365/start-make-rsps-online-detailed-769649/]http://forum.ragezone.com/f365/start-make-rsps-online-detailed-769649/[/url]
